    tag: "Beach",
    summary: "Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Panama City Beach! This stunning property offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, & beachside living. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from the pristine beaches, vibrant local attractions, and excellent dining options that make Panama City Beach a sought-after destination.\n\nNearby Attractions\n- Frank Brown Park\n- Pier Park\n- Russell-Fields Pier\n- Conservation Park\n- Gulf World Marine Park\n- Panama City Beach Winery",
    description: "KEY FEATURES:\n\nSPACIOUS LIVING\n- 4 Bedrooms\n- 2 Bathrooms\n- Open-concept floor plan\n\nMODERN KITCHEN:\n- Granite countertops\n- Stainless steel appliances\n- Custom cabinetry\n- Large island with seating\n\nOUTDOOR OASIS\n- Private backyard\n- Large patio area\n- Beautifully landscaped garden\n- Room for a pool\n\nADDITIONAL HIGHLIGHTS\n- Hardwood floors throughout\n- High ceilings\n- Ample natural light\n- Two-car garage\n- Energy-efficient windows and appliances\n\nLOCATION\nLocated in the desirable Chelsea Drive community, this home is perfect for families and retirees alike. Enjoy easy access to local schools, parks, and shopping centers. The famous white-sand beaches of the Gulf Coast are just a short drive away, offering endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.\n\n‼️NO WASHER & DRYER ACCESS‼️\n\nThe guest will have access to the entire property during their stay. Guests will also have access to the public beach.\n\nGuests can contact us anytime, we have 24/7 support team.\n\nNestled in the heart of Panama City Beach, the Chelsea Drive neighborhood is a tranquil and charming residential area that offers a perfect blend of coastal living and suburban convenience. This community is highly sought after for its serene atmosphere, beautiful homes, and close proximity to some of the best attractions and amenities in the region.\n\nCommunity Atmosphere:\nThe Chelsea Drive neighborhood boasts a warm and welcoming atmosphere where neighbors know each other by name. Tree-lined streets, well-maintained lawns, and a sense of pride in homeownership are evident throughout the area. It's a place where families, retirees, and professionals alike can find a peaceful retreat away from the hustle and bustle, yet still enjoy the vibrant lifestyle that Panama City Beach has to offer.\n\nProximity to Attractions:\nLiving in the Chelsea Drive neighborhood means being just minutes away from the stunning white-sand beaches of the Gulf Coast. Residents can easily spend their weekends sunbathing, swimming, or enjoying water sports. Additionally, the popular Pier Park, with its array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, is just a short drive away. Whether you're looking to explore nature at Conservation Park, have fun with the family at Shipwreck Island Waterpark, or enjoy a day of fishing at Russell-Fields Pier, everything is within easy reach.\n\nConvenient Amenities:\nThe neighborhood is conveniently located near top-rated schools, making it an ideal place for families. Grocery stores, healthcare facilities, and fitness centers are also nearby, ensuring that residents have everything they need within a short distance. For those who enjoy an active lifestyle, Frank Brown Park offers sports facilities, walking trails, and community events throughout the year.\n\nNEARBY ATTRACTIONS:\nFrank Brown Park\nA community park offering sports facilities, an aquatic center, playgrounds, and nature trails. (About 1 mile away)\n\nPier Park\nA premier shopping and entertainment destination featuring a variety of shops, restaurants, a movie theater, and live music events. (About 2 miles away)\n\nRussell-Fields Pier\nA popular spot for fishing, strolling, and enjoying panoramic views of the Gulf of Mexico. (About 2 miles away)\n\nConservation Park\nA beautiful park with over 24 miles of trails for hiking and biking, along with scenic boardwalks through wetlands. (About 3 miles away)\n\nGulf World Marine Park\nEnjoy interactive programs, dolphin shows, and exhibits showcasing marine life, perfect for a family-friendly day out. (About 3 miles away)\n\nPanama City Beach Winery\nA unique winery offering tropical fruit wines and a cozy tasting room, perfect for a relaxing afternoon. (About 5 miles away)\n\nShipwreck Island Waterpark\nA thrilling waterpark featuring wave pools, lazy rivers, and numerous water slides, ideal for cooling off on a hot day. (About 6 miles away)\n\nWonderWorks\nAn interactive amusement park with over 100 hands-on science exhibits, a ropes course, and a laser tag arena. (About 6 miles away)\n\nRipley's Believe It or Not!\nAn odditorium with bizarre exhibits, a 7D moving theater, and a laser race, providing fun for all ages. (About 6 miles away)\n\nSt. Andrews State Park\nA natural paradise offering stunning beaches, nature trails, picnic areas, and opportunities for swimming, snorkeling, and kayaking. (About 12 miles away)\n\n📌 Note: Extra guest fee of $20/guest per night applies from the 5th guest onwards. Base price only covers the first 4 guests.",
