    description: "Horizon Luxury Rentals has taken care of every detail so you can enjoy your stay in Nashville.  \n\nSome Key Features:\n\nLiving Room  \n✧ 65” Smart TV with Netflix, Prime Video, Hulu  \n✧ Comfortable designer sofa  \n✧ Professional standing desk with desk lamp and chair  \n✧ Aesthetic lighting  \n✧ Throw blanket  \n✧ Stylish decor  \n\nKitchen  \n✧ Stainless steel appliances  \n✧ Coffee options: Keurig, French press, pour-over, coffee maker, K-cups, and ground coffee  \n✧ Small appliances: Toaster, blender, gooseneck kettle  \n✧ Cooking essentials: Pots and pans, baking sheets, utensils, mixing bowls, measuring cups, spices, oil, grilling tools  \n✧ Eating essentials: Plates, bowls, silverware, glasses, mugs, wine glasses  \n✧ Table with 4 chairs  \n✧ In-unit washer and dryer  \n\nBedroom  \n✧ Comfortable memory foam mattress with mattress protector  \n✧ 2 down alternative pillows, 2 memory foam pillows, pillow protectors  \n✧ Premium sheets  \n✧ Wireless phone charger  \n✧ 55” Smart TV with Netflix, Prime Video, Hulu  \n✧ Nightstands with stylish lamps  \n\nBathroom  \n✧ Luxurious towels  \n✧ Glass shower  \n✧ Essential toiletries: Shampoo, conditioner, body wash, toothpaste, mouthwash, bathroom cups, Q-tips, soap  \n✧ Toilet paper  \n✧ Hand soap  \n✧ Hair dryer  \n\nCloset  \n✧ Extra blanket  \n✧ Dresser  \n✧ Hangers  \n✧ Steamer  \n✧ Iron and ironing board  \n✧ Vacuum  \n✧ Steam mop  \n✧ Cleaning supplies: Lysol, Clorox, Windex, cleaning rags, detergent  \n\nOther Features  \n✧ High-speed WiFi  \n✧ Free parking in parking garage  \n\nCommunity  \n✧ Rooftop pool with stunning views  \n✧ State-of-the-art gym  \n✧ Community outdoor areas  \n✧ Co-working space  \n✧ Package room  \n✧ 24/7 concierge service  \n\nLocation  \n✧ Walking distance to restaurants: Jason’s Deli, Cinco De Mayo, Five Guys, Amerigo, Poindexter Coffee  \n✧ Within close proximity to Vanderbilt University, Centennial Park, Downtown Nashville",
