    summary: "Family-friendly 3BR home in Glendale/LA, 15 min from Universal Studios, Hollywood, and DTLA. Sleeps 9 with game room, PacMan arcade, ping-pong, backyard pool, and fire pit.\n\nCentrally located near Griffith Observatory, Dodger Stadium, Burbank studios, and LA Convention Center. Quiet, tree-lined neighborhood. Exact address provided after booking (S Hudson Ave and Dockweiler St area). Free parking and high-speed WiFi.\n\nNote: Duplex with one shared wall to adjacent unit.",
    description: "1st Bedroom: 1 Cal-King Bed\n\n2nd Bedroom: 2 Queen Beds\n\n3rd Guest Room/Office Attached to 2nd Bedroom: 1 Daybed + Workspace\n\n4th Sleeping Area Adjacent to Living Room: Queen Sized Air Mattress Available\n\nThis home is a duplex, with your neighbor being another Airbnb guest on vacation.\n\nSelf check-in via smart lock for flexible arrival. Our hosting team is available 24/7 via the Airbnb app or phone. We provide full privacy during your stay and respond promptly to any questions or requests. Happy to share local dining recommendations and tips for exploring the area.\n\nMy family and I live just a few houses away so if you need anything, we won't be far!\n\nSurrounded by multi-million dollar homes, you will be staying in a quiet and safe neighborhood where there will always be a friendly face walking their four-legged friend!\n\n2 Parking Spots are available at the home, but if any additional guests need, there is ample, non-permitted street parking. The Big Blue bus stop is walking distance from the home and is a straight shot to the Santa Monica Pier and the beach! Other public transportation lines such as the Metro Bus and Subway are less than a mile away!\n\nLOCATION: We are located 15-20 minutes away from all the famous sights around LA. See the full list below with exact distances from attractions!\n\n🅿️ Tight driveway parking is available on a first-come-first-serve basis, however, plenty of free street parking\n\n\n📣 NOISE: Please note this is a Duplex with 1 shared wall to another Airbnb home. There is a potential for noise with the unit next door.\n‼️We have noise monitors in the house‼️\n\nBACKYARD: This space is shared with 1 other Airbnb unit.\n\nLA Attractions:\n\n- Universal Studios Hollywood: 14 min drive (6.5 miles)\n\n- Crypto Arena: 13 min drive (6.2 miles away)\n\n- LA Convention Center/Downtown LA: 13 min drive (6.4 miles away)\n\n- Sofi Stadium/The Forum: 19 min drive (7.9 miles away)\n\n- Banc of California Stadium: 12 min drive (6.6 miles)\n\n- Beverly Hills/Rodeo Drive: 15 min drive (4.4 miles)\n\n- Hollywood Walk of Fame: 12 min (3.8 miles away)\n\n- Santa Monica Pier: 16 min drive (11 miles)\n\n- Venice Beach Boardwalk: 19 min drive (12 miles)\n\n- West Hollywood: 13 min drive (4.5 miles away)\n\n- Griffith Observatory/Hollywood Sign/LA Zoo: 20 min drive (11 miles away)\n\n- Disneyland: 35 mins (32 miles away)\n\n\nStores and Essentials:\n\n- Ralph's Grocery Store: 0.4 miles away\n\n- Target: 0.7 miles away\n\n- CVS Pharmacy: 0.5 miles away\n\n- Ross: 0.3 miles away\n\n- Sprouts: 0.8 miles away\n\n- Lassens: 1.4 miles away\n\nABSOLUTELY NO EVENTS. Birthdays included!\n\nPlease note: Guests must be at least 25 years old to book this property.",
