    tag: "Florida",
    summary: "Remodeled 4BR home in Palm Beach Gardens with private pool, movie room, and in-law suite. Minutes from Juno Beach, Jupiter Beach, and PGA National Golf Resort. Sleeps 10 - perfect for families, golf trips, and extended stays.\n\nDedicated home office, fully equipped kitchen, spacious backyard, and serene setting. Near Downtown Palm Beach Gardens, The Gardens Mall, Roger Dean Stadium, and Downtown West Palm Beach. Free parking, high-speed WiFi, and washer/dryer included.",
