    summary: "Bonita Bay condo with private beach club access and complimentary shuttle to the Gulf Coast shoreline. Located in Bonita Springs, minutes from Naples, Fort Myers, and Sanibel Island.\n\nBright, comfortable unit with modern finishes. Exclusive resort amenities including beach shuttle, pools, tennis, and golf. Near Coconut Point Mall, Miromar Outlets, and Southwest Florida International Airport. Perfect for beach vacations, golf trips, and snowbird stays.",
    description: "Enjoy peaceful mornings on the private balcony, fun afternoons by the community pool, and evenings exploring the Promenade at Bonita Bay—just minutes away, featuring upscale shops, amazing restaurants, and vibrant local culture!\n\n🛒 Need groceries or a quick bite? You’re in luck! Across the street, you'll find Publix, The Fresh Market, HomeGoods, and even Audi Bonita Springs for car enthusiasts. Don’t miss DiRomio’s Italian Market & Restaurant—a local favorite for authentic Italian eats!\n\n🏡 What You'll Love:\n📍 Prime location in Bonita Bay, close to restaurants, shops & top attractions\n\n🏖️ Only minutes from Bonita Beach & Barefoot Beach Preserve\n\n🛒 Walkable to grocery stores, cafes, markets & more\n\n🌿 Surrounded by nature preserves and walking trails\n\n☕ Perfect for families, couples, snowbirds & remote workers!\n\n🛏️ The Space:\nPrimary Suite: Queen bed, Smart TV & en-suite bathroom\n\nGuest Bedroom: 1 Queen bed + 1 Bunk bed (2 Twin mattresses)\n\nLiving Room: Spacious sofa, 55\" Smart TV, board games & balcony access\n\nKitchen: Fully stocked open-plan kitchen with modern appliances\n\nDining: Indoor table for 6 & balcony dining set for 6\n\n🌟 Amenities:\n🏊‍♀️ Community Pool\n\n💦 Hot Tub\n\n🍔 BBQ Grill\n\n🚗 Free Parking on Premises\n\n🧺 Stackable Washer & Dryer\n\n📺 2 Smart TVs\n\n📶 High-Speed WiFi\n\n🌅 Balcony w/ Sofa, Egg Chair & 6-Seater Dining Area\n\n☕ Coffee Maker\n\n🍽️ Dishwasher, Oven, Microwave, Stove & Full-size Fridge\n\n🎲 Board Games for the whole family!\n\n📍 Nearby Attractions:\nPromenade at Bonita Bay – 2 mins\n\nBarefoot Beach Preserve – 12 mins\n\nBonita Beach Park – 10 mins\n\nRiverside Park – 7 mins\n\nNaples Downtown – 25 mins\n\nCoconut Point Mall – 15 mins\n\nMiromar Outlets – 20 mins\n\nSouthwest Florida International Airport (RSW) – 25 mins\n\nExciting News! Guests will soon have access to a brand-new, exclusive private beach and beach club, currently in its final stages of a $7 million renovation—set to be completed this month! Enjoy upgraded amenities, modern design, and a luxurious waterfront experience just steps away from your stay.\n\nWhether you’re soaking up the sun, enjoying a sunset on the balcony, or exploring the charm of Bonita Springs, this condo has everything to make your stay unforgettable. 🌴\n\n🗓️ Book your stay today and experience the best of Bonita Bay living!\n\nThe whole condo is located on the first floor only.\n\nSelf check-in via smart lock for flexible arrival. Our hosting team is available 24/7 via the Airbnb app or phone. We provide full privacy during your stay and respond promptly to any questions or requests. Happy to share local dining recommendations and tips for exploring the area.\n\n🏡 Neighborhood Overview – Bonita Bay, Bonita Springs, FL\nBonita Bay is one of the most prestigious and peaceful gated communities in Bonita Springs. Known for its lush landscapes, walking and biking trails, and beautiful nature preserves, it offers the perfect blend of relaxation and convenience.\n\nLocated just minutes from Bonita Beach and Barefoot Beach, you’re never far from the Gulf’s crystal-clear waters and soft sandy shores. The Promenade at Bonita Bay is just around the corner—an open-air shopping and dining destination featuring everything from casual bites to fine dining, local boutiques, and weekend farmers markets.\n\nRight across the street from the complex, you'll find a Publix supermarket, HomeGoods, The Fresh Market, and even an Audi dealership—making everyday essentials and spontaneous cravings super convenient.\n\n🚗 Getting Around\nCar Recommended: While many essentials are walkable, having a car is the best way to explore the beaches, nearby parks, Naples, and Fort Myers.\n\nFree Parking: Complimentary parking is available on the premises.\n\nUber/Lyft: Readily available and reliable in the area.\n\nBike-Friendly: Bonita Bay has scenic bike paths and trails perfect for cycling enthusiasts.\n\nAirport Access: Just 25 minutes to Southwest Florida International Airport (RSW) for easy arrivals and departures.\n\nWhether you want to stroll to dinner or take a day trip down the coast, Bonita Bay is the perfect base for your Florida getaway! 🌴✨\n\n📌 Note: Extra guest fee of $20/guest per night applies from the 3rd guest onwards. Base price only covers the first 2 guests.",
