    summary: "Welcome to your home away from home in Jacksonville, Florida! 🌊\nA single level home with over 1900+ sq ft of living space! ✨\n\nThis spacious retreat offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience—whether you’re visiting for family fun, a beach escape, or a work trip. ☀️\n\nWith plenty of room to relax, modern amenities, and community pool access, this stay is designed for both comfort and connection. 🌼",
    description: "The space\n\n-   2 bedrooms with a king size bed each + shared bathroom\n-   1 master bedroom with 2 Queen size beds + ensuite bathroom\n-   2 Living Rooms with 65\" Smart TV\n-   Shared Community Pool\n-   Kitchen & Dining fully equipped with appliances\n-   Washer and dryer\n\n🏙️ Neighborhood Highlights\nOur home is conveniently located in Jacksonville with easy access to some of the city’s best spots:\n\n🛍️ St. Johns Town Center Mall (4790 River City Dr) – Jacksonville’s premier shopping and dining destination.\n\n🥑 Whole Foods Market (10601 San Jose Blvd) – perfect for fresh groceries and healthy essentials.\n\n🍽️ Riverside & Downtown Jacksonville – a hub for trendy restaurants, craft breweries, and nightlife.\n\n🏈 EverBank Stadium – catch exciting events, concerts, and Jaguars games.\n\n🏥 Mayo Clinic Jacksonville – a short drive for guests traveling for medical care.\n✈️ Naval Air Station Jacksonville (NAS JAX) – convenient for military families and professionals.\n\nYou can access the entire place.\n\nWe love to communicate to our guests here on Airbnb! Just message us if you have further questions.\n\n🌟 Endless Fun Nearby! 🌟\nStay close to it all—Old Town & Fun Spot America for rides and family fun, World Food Trucks for global eats, Pirates Island Golf for mini-golf adventures, plus Boggy Creek Airboat Rides and Wild Florida Safari for unforgettable outdoor thrills. Shoppers will love The Loop & Plaza del Sol, while history buffs can explore the Osceola History Museum. Something for everyone—just minutes from your stay!\n\n🌟 Explore the Best of Kissimmee Nearby! 🌟\nYou’ll be just minutes from all the fun:\n\n🎡 Old Town & Fun Spot America – rides, shops & classic car shows (5 mins)\n\n🌮 World Food Trucks – 50+ global flavors to try (5 mins)\n\n📌 Pirates Island Adventure Golf – family mini-golf fun (6 mins)\n\n🛶 Boggy Creek Airboat Adventures – glide through Florida wetlands (20 mins)\n\n🐊 Wild Florida Safari Park – gators, wildlife & a drive-thru safari (40 mins)\n\n🛍️ The Loop Outdoor Mall – shopping, dining & movies (10 mins)\n\n🛒 Plaza del Sol Indoor Mall – shops, eats & outlets (12 mins)\n\n🏞️ Osceola History Museum & Nature Preserve – culture & trails (15 mins)\n\n✨ Kissimmee Prairie Preserve State Park – stargazing & nature escapes (1 hr)\n\nFrom thrill rides to wildlife adventures and shopping sprees, everything is close by—making your stay the perfect launchpad for Central Florida fun! 🌴\n\n📌 Note: Extra guest fee of $20/guest per night applies from the 4th guest onwards. Base price only covers 3 guests.",
