    description: "🛏️ This single-level beach condo is designed for comfort and convenience! \n\n🛏️ Sleeping Arrangements & Condo Perks\n\nBedroom 1: King bed + TV\nBedroom 2: Queen bed + TV\nBedroom 3: Queen bed + TV\nExtra: Queen air mattress available for added flexibility\n\nPerfect for families or groups. With first-floor access directly to the beach, the Gulf is literally at your doorstep. 🌊✨ \n\nLocated in Pinnacle Port/Carillon Beach, a private and secure community, you’ll enjoy resort-style amenities: \n- 2 pools (including a covered pool)\n- Gym\n- Library\n- Boat Ramp\n- Fishing (they’ll even clean your catch for a small fee 🎣)\n- Basketball and tennis courts\n- BBQ grills.\n\n🍴 Within Carillon Beach, you’ll find restaurants, bike rentals, and even a church—no need to drive far! \n\n🚗 3 minutes away:\n✓ Publix\n✓ Aldi\n✓ Wells Fargo\n\n☕ 5 minutes away: Local coffee & donuts\n\n🛍 20 minutes away: Pier Park’s shopping, dining & movie theaters\n\n🌳 Nature escape: Camp Helen State Park (just across the bridge)\nMore restaurants & boutique shops to explore and Destin’s famous outlet mall\n\nYou’ll have full access to the condo during your stay—treat it like your own and have an amazing time! 🏡✨\n\nYou can contact us anytime via the Airbnb app or through our contact number.\n\n🌴 Neighborhood\n\nStay right on Front Beach Road, where the beach is just steps away and everything you need is close by. \n\nYou’ll be minutes from Pier Park for shopping, dining, and entertainment, plus plenty of local seafood spots, beach bars, and family attractions. Getting around is easy—walk, bike, or take a quick drive to explore all that Panama City Beach has to offer!\n\n🍴 Within Carillon Beach, you’ll find restaurants, bike rentals, and even a church—no need to drive far! \n\n🚗 3 minutes away:\n✓ Publix\n✓ Aldi\n✓ Wells Fargo\n\n☕ 5 minutes away: Local coffee & donuts\n\n🛍 20 minutes away: Pier Park’s shopping, dining & movie theaters\n\n🌳 Nature escape: Camp Helen State Park (just across the bridge)\nMore restaurants & boutique shops to explore and Destin’s famous outlet mall\n\n📌 Note: Extra guest fee of $20/guest per night applies from the 4th guests onwards. Base price only covers the 3 guest.\n\nA resort fee will be need to be paid and a photo ID",
