    price: 100,
    tag: "Home",
    summary: "Welcome to your Southside Slopes retreat! This spacious 3BR/3BA home comfortably hosts up to 12 guests, perfect for family trips or group getaways. \n\nEnjoy a modern kitchen, open living areas, hardwood floors, and a cozy fireplace. Relax on the deck or in the fenced yard. \n\nJust minutes from lively Carson St, downtown Pittsburgh, and major attractions, this stylish home offers both comfort and convenience for your stay.",
    description: "Welcome to Your Pittsburgh Getaway!\n\nThis spacious South Side home offers comfort, convenience, and plenty of room for your group to relax and make lasting memories. Whether you’re here for family time, a friends’ trip, or a special celebration, this property is designed to host up to 12 guests with ease.\n\n🎮 Entertainment & Living Spaces\n✦ Spacious living room with 2 sleeper chairs + a full sofa sleeper\n✦ Large Smart TV for streaming your favorite shows\n✦ Comfortable lounge area for family gatherings or game nights\n\n🛏️ Sleep & Stay in Comfort (Sleeps up to 12)\n✦ Bedroom 1 – King bed \n✦ Bedroom 2 – Queen bed + futon\n✦ Bedroom 3 – Bunk bed with pull out bed with trundle (sleeps 4)\n✦ Living Room – 2 sleeper chairs + 1 sofa sleeper\n\n🧼 Bathrooms\n✦ Full bathrooms stocked with essentials\n✦ Fresh towels and starter toiletries provided\n\n🍳 Full Kitchen\n✦ Fully equipped with modern appliances\n✦ Coffee maker & essentials for your morning brew\n✦ Cookware, dinnerware, and utensils included\n\n🍽️ Dining Area\n✦ Seating for group meals around the dining table and kitchen bar\n✦ Open layout perfect for gathering together\n\n💼 Work-Ready for Remote Guests\n✦ High-speed WiFi – perfect for Zoom calls, streaming, or both\n✦ Desks and tables available for work or study needs\n\n📍 Prime Location – South Side Slopes\nStay in the heart of Pittsburgh’s South Side, just minutes from top attractions:\n✅ South Side Flats – 0.5 miles (shopping, dining, nightlife)\n✅ Carson Street – 0.6 miles\n✅ Station Square – 1.2 miles\n✅ PPG Paints Arena – 1.4 miles\n✅ Downtown Pittsburgh – 1.8 miles\n✅ Point State Park – 2 miles\n✅ Acrisure Stadium (Steelers) – 3 miles\n✅ PNC Park (Pirates) – 3 miles\n✅ Mount Washington Overlook – 3 miles\n✅ University of Pittsburgh / Carnegie Mellon – 4 miles\n\n🛒 Nearby Shopping & Essentials\n✅ Giant Eagle – 1.5 miles\n✅ Target – 2.2 miles\n✅ Walgreens – 1.2 miles\n✅ Whole Foods – 4.5 miles\n✅ SouthSide Works shopping + dining – 1 mile\n\n✨ Whether you’re here for a game, a night out on Carson Street, or simply to explore all that Pittsburgh has to offer, this home has the space, comfort, and location to make your stay unforgettable.\n\nGuest will have access to the entire house and all of its amenities.\n\nThis property is equipped with a smart lock, front door Ring doorbell camera, and noise monitor\n\nWe can communicate via Airbnb 📲\n\nJust minutes from lively Carson St, downtown Pittsburgh, and major attractions, this stylish home offers both comfort and convenience for your stay.\n\n📍 Prime Location – South Side Slopes\nStay in the heart of Pittsburgh’s South Side, just minutes from top attractions:\n✅ South Side Flats – 0.5 miles (shopping, dining, nightlife)\n✅ Carson Street – 0.6 miles\n✅ Station Square – 1.2 miles\n✅ PPG Paints Arena – 1.4 miles\n✅ Downtown Pittsburgh – 1.8 miles\n✅ Point State Park – 2 miles\n✅ Acrisure Stadium (Steelers) – 3 miles\n✅ PNC Park (Pirates) – 3 miles\n✅ Mount Washington Overlook – 3 miles\n✅ University of Pittsburgh / Carnegie Mellon – 4 miles\n\n🛒 Nearby Shopping & Essentials\n✅ Giant Eagle – 1.5 miles\n✅ Target – 2.2 miles\n✅ Walgreens – 1.2 miles\n✅ Whole Foods – 4.5 miles\n✅ SouthSide Works shopping + dining – 1 mile\n\nOur home is nestled in a residential neighborhood. There are noise restrictions with quiet hours from 10 pm to 8 am. This is enforced by the city.\n\nA gentle reminder, there is absolutely no smoking inside the property. No parties are allowed. A minimum fee of $300 will be applied for any violations of the house rules.\n\n🅿️ Parking\nStreet parking is available directly across from the home, since the road in front is one-way. 🚗✨\n\n🚫 Parties are not allowed.\n\n📌 Extra guest fee of $20/guest per night applies from the 4th guest onwards. Base price only covers the first 3 guests.",
