    summary: "NEWLY UPDATED Luxurious Gated Private Waterfront Estate 7000 SF Quiet Tranquil\n\n⭐️NEWLY UPDATED!!⭐️\nAs of 2024, the property underwent a massive exterior rejuvenation with new poolside furniture, a resurfaced pool, and a completely washed and updated exterior!\n\nPerfect for a family vacation or corporate retreat!\n\n‼️ Note: The boat is NOT part of the rental. It's rented out to different guests who uses part of the property for parking only.",
    description: "This spectacular waterfront Mediterranean masterpiece has 7000 . of living space. The home is exquisitely appointed with the finest of materials and craftsmanship, providing you with the warmth of a home away from home.\n\nFeel the stress leave as you drive into the one-acre estate through a canopy of grand oaks. Seclude yourself in this gated sanctuary while still being in the center of it all. Enjoy the expansive waterfront from almost every room of the villa. Large enough to provide privacy to each member of your group and yet provide plenty of space to eat, drink and be merry together. Enjoy the spacious pool deck between laps in the extra-large heated pool or just relax on the covered patio with a drink and watch the boats go by.\n\nWe just installed a brand new mesh network so if you do have to do a little work while you're staying, you will have a strong internet connection.\n\n*Our property is located in a quiet family neighborhood. We love hosting family vacations for up to 12 people, but we are not suitable for parties or events. We strive to always keep our home in tip-top condition and don't allow more than 12 guests at any time. We also do not allow visitors who are not registered with us.*\n\nThe villa's six bedrooms all have an attached full bathroom. The bathrooms are all appointed with ample linens.\n\nThere is a television in every bedroom, along with a large TV in the family room. The TVs all had Roku or Fire TV Stick.\n\nWe also provide beach towels, paper towels, trash bags, shampoo, conditioner, body wash, hand soap, laundry detergent, dish and dishwasher detergent, coffee and coffee filters, salt and pepper, spices, hair dryers, an iron, and an ironing board.\n\nKeywords: Serene, Quiet, Corporate Retreat, Tranquil, Gated, Old World Mediterranean, Mediterranean Masterpiece, Peaceful, Retreat, Spacious Pool, Dock, Boat, Waterfront, Luxury, Luxe, Luxury Property, Classic, Classy, Tranquil, Luxury, Luxurious, Mansion, Gated, Estate, Glamorous, Family Vacation, Quiet Getaway, Luxurious Stay, Luxury Vacation\n\nWe have 7 exterior cameras covering N,S,E, & W sides of the home, driveway and dock areas.\nOur prices include all fees. No hidden fees.\n\nGuest will have access to the entire property during their stay.\n\nGuests can reach out to us via Airbnb anytime.\n\n✅ Because this is a higher-end neighborhood, expectations around finishes, security (gated access) and amenities (e.g., outdoor spaces, pool, landscaping) are elevated. Align your listing text and property presentation accordingly.\n\n✅ While close to downtown, guests should still be oriented to local commute/traffic times and transport options (especially at peak times) to avoid surprises.\n\n✅ For family-friendly stays, it’s worth noting the assigned local schools: e.g., Stranahan High School, which for some families may reflect the broader neighborhood standard.\n\nGetting around is effortless: we’re just a short 10-minute drive from Las Olas Boulevard and 15 minutes from the beach. Uber/Lyft rides are plentiful from the gate. If you have your own car we’ll send detailed parking/garage instructions. \n\nPrefer water travel? The estate fronts the New River and offers private boat dock access—perfect for a twilight cruise or water-taxi into downtown. \n\nPublic bus stop is nearby via Broward County Transit for budget-minded guests, though a car or ride-share is recommended for full convenience.\n\n✅ Extra-person charges may apply and vary depending on property policy\n\n✅ Special requests are subject to availability upon check-in and may incur additional charges; special requests cannot be guaranteed\n\n✅ Onsite parties or group events are strictly prohibited\n\n✅ Host has indicated there is a carbon monoxide detector on the property\n\n✅ Host has indicated there is a smoke detector on the property\n\n✅ Safety features at this property include a fire extinguisher and a deadbolt lock",
