    description: "🏡 Home Layout\n\nDownstairs\n\n🛏️ Master bedroom with king bed + private ensuite bathroom\n\n🚻 Half bathroom\n\n🍽️ Kitchen, 🍴 dining area, and 🛋️ main living room\n\nUpstairs\n\n🛋️ Second living room / loft area\n\n🛏️ Bedroom 1: Bunk bed + double bed\n🛏️ Bedroom 2: Queen bed\n🛏️ Bedroom 3: King bed\n🛏️ Bedroom 4: Queen bed\n\n🚿 Two full bathrooms shared between upstairs bedrooms\n\n🏊‍♂️ Private pool\n🌞 Sun loungers for relaxing\n🪑 Cozy outdoor seating area\n🍖 Grill for outdoor cooking and BBQs \n\n📍 Nearby Attractions\n\n🌳 Crescent Bend Nature Park — approx 3.5 miles\n🛍️ Grange Farmers & Artisans Market — approx 2–3 miles\n🏞️ Niagara Park — approx 2 miles\n\n🍽️ Nearby Restaurants\n\n🍕 Catalano’s Pizzeria — approx 3 miles\n☕ Cibolo Coffee Haus — approx 2.5 miles\n🍔 Whataburger (Cibolo Valley Dr) — approx 3 miles\n\n🛒 Grocery Stores\n\n🥬 H-E-B (Cibolo) — approx 4 miles\n🛒 Pic-N-Pac Convenience Store — approx 2 miles\nOutdoor Area\n\nGuests have full access to the entire home, including all bedrooms, living areas, and outdoor spaces. Self check-in is available for your convenience, so you can arrive at any time after check-in begins and let yourself in easily using the provided door code. Enjoy complete privacy and make yourself at home!\n\nWe respect your privacy and give you the space to enjoy your stay, but we’re just a message or phone call away if you need anything. Whether it’s questions about the home, local recommendations, or anything that comes up during your visit, we’re happy to help and make sure you have a comfortable stay!\n\nThe home is located in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood in Cibolo, TX, just a short drive from parks, shops, and local restaurants. You’ll enjoy peaceful streets, nearby green spaces, and easy access to everything you need for a comfortable stay. Whether you want to explore nature, grab a bite to eat, or just relax at home, this neighborhood offers the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility.\n\n🚗 Getting Around\n\nThe neighborhood is easy to navigate by car, with plenty of nearby parking for guests. Most attractions, restaurants, and grocery stores are just a short drive away. Rideshare services like Uber and Lyft are also available in the area for added convenience. Walking and biking are ideal for nearby parks and local streets, but a car is recommended for exploring the wider area.\n\n📌 Note: Extra guest fee of $20 per guest per night applies from the 5th guest onwards. Base price only covers the first 5 guests.",
