    summary: "Luxury 12BR mansion in Kissimmee, minutes from Disney and Orlando attractions. Ideal for large groups, reunions, and retreats.\n\nPrivate heated pool/spa, game room, and FREE resort with waterslide, splash pad, hot tub, and gym. All 12 bedrooms have a private bath and Smart TV.\n\nHighlights:\n- Custom-themed bedrooms with lake views\n- High-speed Wi-Fi\n- BBQ grill and spacious backyard\n- FREE baby gear (high chair, pack n play, stroller)\n- Local vendor partner discounts",
    description: "Secure keyless entry via smart lock.\n\nKITCHEN: Two full refrigerators, two dishwashers, fully equipped for large group cooking. Full-sized washer and dryer included.\n\nSLEEPING (12 BR / 13 beds):\nFirst Floor: 1 King, 3 Queens\nSecond Floor: 5 Kings, plus themed kids rooms (Zootopia, Despicable Me, Wreck-it Ralph, Tangled, Lilo and Stitch) with bunks and twins.\n\nDINING: Indoor table seats 16, kitchen island seats 5, patio dining seats 10.\n\nOUTDOOR: Private heated pool and spa, patio furniture for 15+, sun loungers.\n\nRESORT ACCESS (FREE): Waterslide, splash pad, resort pool, hot tub, gym, and clubhouse. Perfect after a day at Disney World, Universal Studios, or SeaWorld.\n\nGAME ROOM: Arcade games, pool table, and entertainment for all ages.\n\nFull access to the entire 12-bedroom mansion, private heated pool/spa, game room, and all resort amenities including waterslide, splash pad, pool, hot tub, and gym. Self check-in via digital smart lock. The community is gated with 24-hour attendants — please have ID and reservation confirmation ready for entry after hours. Free parking for multiple vehicles in the driveway.\n\nWe offer self check-in with keyless smart lock for flexible arrival. Our hosting team is available 24/7 via the Airbnb app or phone for any questions during your stay. We provide a detailed digital guidebook with tips on nearby Disney World restaurants, Universal Studios planning, outlet mall shopping, and hidden gems in Kissimmee and Orlando. We love helping guests plan the perfect Florida vacation!\n\nVeranda Palms Resort is a prestigious collection of Single Family Homes, only 12 minutes from Walt Disney World's entrance! Enjoy the Resort Clubhouse with fantastic amenities, including children's playgrounds and a resort-style pool. Plus, stay active with our fitness center!\n\nWe strongly advise renting a car to explore Orlando Metro Area.\n\nNearby attractions:\n- Walt Disney World (15 min)\n- Universal Studios Orlando (20 min)\n- SeaWorld Orlando (20 min)\n- LEGOLAND Florida (30 min)\n- Orlando Premium Outlets (10 min)\n- International Drive dining and entertainment (15 min)\n- Kissimmee Lakefront Park (10 min)\n- Orlando International Airport (25 min)\n- Celebration, FL (10 min)\n\nExtra guest fee: $50/person per night from the 11th guest onwards. Airbnb allows up to 16 guests on the reservation; additional guest fees collected separately after booking confirmation.",
